1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,509
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,979
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,159
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,399
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,729
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,319
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,609
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,059
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,289
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,709
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,199
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,749
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,169
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,999
=No Way! My Bro is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,160
=Episode 6=

19
00:01:11,830 --> 00:01:13,200
If you want him released, you do it.

20
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:14,920
I

21
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,320
won't.

22
00:01:18,010 --> 00:01:19,150
Your Majesty...

23
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:22,990
My apologies.

24
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,470
I suppose

25
00:01:24,590 --> 00:01:26,720
Official Lu is cursing me in prison

26
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:27,629
for ruining

27
00:01:27,630 --> 00:01:29,950
his and General Sun's plan.

28
00:01:30,730 --> 00:01:31,989
How is that my concern?

29
00:01:31,990 --> 00:01:33,040
Isn't it?

30
00:01:33,350 --> 00:01:34,469
You've been defeating

31
00:01:34,470 --> 00:01:36,149
that scoundrel.

32
00:01:36,150 --> 00:01:36,629
I figured

33
00:01:36,630 --> 00:01:38,730
you two had some kind
of corrupt deal going on.

34
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:41,989
You two aren't... What's the phrase?

35
00:01:41,990 --> 00:01:42,949
In

36
00:01:42,950 --> 00:01:44,240
kahoot...

37
00:01:45,070 --> 00:01:46,309
In cahoots.

38
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,230
That's it.

39
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,950
Watch your mouth.

40
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,069
If you're not involved,

41
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:53,350
then drop it.

42
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,499
Whether he's guilty

43
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:56,200
is for His Majesty

44
00:01:56,350 --> 00:01:58,050
to decide.

45
00:01:59,390 --> 00:02:00,670
Enough of this.

46
00:02:00,950 --> 00:02:02,160
One more thing.

47
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:05,350
Princess Xiao Ling has come of age.

48
00:02:05,590 --> 00:02:07,560
General Gu has served with distinction.

49
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,670
I intend to marry Princess Xiao Ling

50
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:11,310
to Gu Bei.

51
00:02:11,350 --> 00:02:12,270
Impossible!

52
00:02:12,410 --> 00:02:14,399
Why do you disagree
with everything His Majesty says?

53
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,880
Do you have a contrarian personality?

54
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,400
Your Majesty,

55
00:02:17,510 --> 00:02:19,629
I've admired Princess Xiaoling for years.

56
00:02:19,630 --> 00:02:20,599
Please consider

57
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,709
my years of service,

58
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:24,720
and grant her hand to me.

59
00:02:24,990 --> 00:02:25,910
I

60
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:28,110
have made my decision.

61
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:38,350
What are you doing?

62
00:02:45,990 --> 00:02:48,000
Every scar I bear

63
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:51,240
was earned fighting for Jing.

64
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:57,520
Our founder

65
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,550
conquered the realm on horseback.

66
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,280
How can the Princess

67
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,830
marry a good-for-nothing?

68
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,080
If Gu Bei

69
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,830
can beat me in combat,

70
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:13,080
I'll gladly concede

71
00:03:13,350 --> 00:03:15,590
and give up her hand.

72
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,739
He's way too skinny.

73
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:28,980
General Sun will kill him.

74
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:31,360
While guarding the border,

75
00:03:31,390 --> 00:03:34,199
I took enemy commanders' heads

76
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:36,430
as easily as taking candy from a baby.

77
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:40,430
Not even an army could wound me.

78
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,870
What's the big deal about scars?

79
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:44,480
The real skill is never getting hurt.

80
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:51,270
I'm willing to duel General Sun
for the sake of the Princess.

81
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:52,990
Since it's a duel,

82
00:03:53,460 --> 00:03:54,950
blades have no eyes.

83
00:03:55,070 --> 00:03:58,430
Let's sign a death waiver first.

84
00:03:59,550 --> 00:04:00,670
No.

85
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:04,990
What?

86
00:04:05,630 --> 00:04:06,670
Are you scared?

87
00:04:08,950 --> 00:04:10,080
Coward.

88
00:04:18,070 --> 00:04:19,200
Let's do this.

89
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:27,710
This is my soft armor.

90
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,759
It'll stop any blade.

91
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:30,870
Wear it tomorrow.

92
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,270
It'll keep you alive.

93
00:04:32,350 --> 00:04:34,109
You're giving this to me?

94
00:04:34,110 --> 00:04:35,360
What about you?

95
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:37,600
I'm just lending it to you.

96
00:04:37,790 --> 00:04:39,789
Let's get through tomorrow first.

97
00:04:39,790 --> 00:04:41,760
No need for that.

98
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,390
With this,

99
00:04:44,010 --> 00:04:46,800
all will be well.

100
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,670
What is this?

101
00:04:49,230 --> 00:04:50,229
I call it

102
00:04:50,230 --> 00:04:54,480
"Close Your Eyes Even When It's Bright"

103
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:55,960
powder.

104
00:04:57,670 --> 00:04:58,789
Tomorrow in the duel,

105
00:04:58,790 --> 00:05:02,320
I'll just blow a little in Sun's face.

106
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:05,080
He won't wake up for a long time.

107
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,600
Whoa.

108
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:22,080
It really works.

109
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:24,279
Xu's been exhausted lately.

110
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,480
He needs some rest.

111
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,190
Greetings, Your Majesty.

112
00:05:29,310 --> 00:05:30,749
Hey, Nan.

113
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:33,199
You even brought me a treat.

114
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,270
You've grown up.

115
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,919
If General Gu's soft armor doesn't fit,

116
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,000
alter it for him.

117
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:42,630
It's for His Majesty...

118
00:05:48,820 --> 00:05:51,960
This is Qinghuan cakes
for His Majesty and you.

119
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,800
General Sun is a formidable fighter.

120
00:05:58,870 --> 00:06:00,800
The armor alone won't be enough.

121
00:06:00,870 --> 00:06:02,479
I'm worried about my brother,

122
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:05,430
so I came to discuss a strategy
with Your Majesty.

123
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,830
Uh...

124
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:21,279
Strategy for me?

125
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:25,920
Looks more like
you came to dote on His Majesty.

126
00:06:31,790 --> 00:06:33,479
Do you like it?

127
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:36,110
I learned it from the imperial chef.

128
00:06:36,550 --> 00:06:37,399
It's good.

129
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,920
A little sweeter would be perfect.

130
00:06:39,670 --> 00:06:41,189
I'll make it again tomorrow.

131
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:43,510
I'll add more sugar.

132
00:06:44,270 --> 00:06:45,180
Sounds good.

133
00:06:45,820 --> 00:06:47,590
If Your Majesty likes it,

134
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:51,160
I'll make it for you every day.

135
00:06:55,190 --> 00:06:56,110
Uh...

136
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:00,599
Really? That seems like a lot of work.

137
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,789
As long as you're happy,

138
00:07:01,790 --> 00:07:03,400
it's no trouble at all.

139
00:07:38,990 --> 00:07:40,960
Take your positions.

140
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:47,579
- Go!
- Go!

141
00:07:47,580 --> 00:07:48,410
Come on!

142
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:58,520
(Round One)

143
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:10,630
Do you know what this is?

144
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,429
I've never amounted to much,

145
00:08:13,430 --> 00:08:14,920
but I spent all my savings

146
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,260
to buy you this silver hairpin.

147
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:21,190
Nan...

148
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:25,360
Consort Nan's life

149
00:08:25,870 --> 00:08:28,550
is in your hands now.

150
00:08:31,870 --> 00:08:33,870
Begin the match.

151
00:08:40,230 --> 00:08:41,670
Wait!

152
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,960
Before we start,

153
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,789
I need to cheer myself up.

154
00:08:47,790 --> 00:08:48,990
Get fired up.

155
00:08:50,010 --> 00:08:51,169
Go, General Gu!

156
00:08:51,170 --> 00:08:52,500
Go, General Gu!

157
00:09:09,750 --> 00:09:12,160
It's the signal we came up with
when we cheated.

158
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,540
(My sister)

159
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,600
(is in trouble.)

160
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:19,640
(Could it be)

161
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,719
(Gu Nan?)

162
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:21,750
Xiao Ling.

163
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:26,360
Go see if Gu Nan is in the palace.

164
00:09:36,190 --> 00:09:37,720
That's enough.

165
00:09:37,950 --> 00:09:38,810
Let's start now.

166
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:47,940
- Go!
- Go!

167
00:09:56,380 --> 00:09:58,239
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

168
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:00,619
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

169
00:10:00,620 --> 00:10:06,059
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

170
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:10,439
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

171
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,849
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

172
00:10:12,850 --> 00:10:15,389
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

173
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:21,059
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

174
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:26,620
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

175
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:32,970
♪Funny moments never stop♪

176
00:10:33,590 --> 00:10:35,780
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

177
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:40,149
♪Yet through every up and down♪

178
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:42,120
♪We create miracles♪

179
00:10:42,420 --> 00:10:44,880
♪From naive youths♪

180
00:10:45,140 --> 00:10:47,619
♪To legendary heroes♪

181
00:10:47,620 --> 00:10:49,569
♪This journey♪

182
00:10:49,570 --> 00:10:53,579
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

183
00:10:53,580 --> 00:10:56,130
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

184
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:01,470
♪Let's create♪

185
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:11,430
♪A legend of our own♪

